{"lang": "ja_JP", "eventid": "act45side", "eventName": "安らかな譫言", "entryType": "ACTIVITY", "storyCode": "SS-6", "avgTag": "戦闘前", "storyName": "反響する大広間", "storyInfo": "散々な姿で夢のお城へと戻ってきた祥子は、メンバーの誰ひとりとして現実世界に戻ることを望んでいないとモーフィアスに嘲笑されてしまう。そしてモーフィアスは祥子のために最高の夢を用意したと告げ、祥子は任務に向かうロドスの車両内でふたたび目覚めることになった。祥子はまた同じ夢の繰り返しかと思っていたが、今回は少し様子が違っていた。\n", "storyList": [{"id": 0, "prop": "HEADER", "attributes": {"key": "title_test", "is_skippable": "true", "fit_mode": "BLACK_MASK"}}, {"id": 1, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 2, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 3, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 4, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "bg_black", "screenadapt": "coverall", "block": "true"}}, {"id": 5, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 6, "prop": "playMusic", "attributes": {"intro": "$darkness02_intro", "key": "$darkness02_loop", "volume": 0.6}}, {"id": 7, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 8, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.5}}, {"id": 9, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "冷たい風が、音を立てて耳元を通り過ぎる。"}}, {"id": 10, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "落ちていく。どんどん速度を上げながら。"}}, {"id": 11, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "しかし、深淵の底にはいまだ辿り着かない。"}}, {"id": 12, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 13, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 14, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 3.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 15, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 16, "prop": "cameraEffect", "attributes": {"effect": "Grayscale", "keep": "true", "amount": 0.5, "fadetime": 0.0}}, {"id": 17, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "bg_lmstreet_1", "screenadapt": "coverall"}}, {"id": 18, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 3.0}}, {"id": 19, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 20, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.5}}, {"id": 21, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4182_oblvns_1#12$2", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 22, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "わたくしが無理難題を突きつけてもついてきてくれるドラマーが他にいまして？", "name": "豊川祥子"}, "figure_art": "avg_4182_oblvns_1#12$2"}, {"id": 23, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4182_oblvns_1#13$2", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 24, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "言いましたわよね。あなたの人生、わたくしにくださると。", "name": "豊川祥子"}, "figure_art": "avg_4182_oblvns_1#13$2"}, {"id": 25, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4182_oblvns_1#13$2", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 26, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "祐天寺さん……あなたは、ただあなたらしくなさって。", "name": "豊川祥子"}, "figure_art": "avg_4182_oblvns_1#13$2"}, {"id": 27, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 28, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 29, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 30, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 31, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "33_g2_srcalley", "screenadapt": "coverall"}}, {"id": 32, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 33, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 34, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.5}}, {"id": 35, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4182_oblvns_1#12$2", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 36, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "自分の居場所を求めて、いくつも組織を渡り歩いてきましたのね。ですが、それでも居場所が見つからないのであれば――", "name": "豊川祥子"}, "figure_art": "avg_4182_oblvns_1#12$2"}, {"id": 37, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4182_oblvns_1#12$2", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 38, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "八幡さん、わたくしと一緒に帰りましょう。", "name": "豊川祥子"}, "figure_art": "avg_4182_oblvns_1#12$2"}, {"id": 39, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4182_oblvns_1#12$2", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 40, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "このような所で苦しむ必要なんてありませんのよ。", "name": "豊川祥子"}, "figure_art": "avg_4182_oblvns_1#12$2"}, {"id": 41, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 42, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 43, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 44, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 45, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "65_g4_islandharbor_n", "screenadapt": "coverall"}}, {"id": 46, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 47, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 48, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.5}}, {"id": 49, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4182_oblvns_1#2$2", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 50, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "初華、あなたがどこにいても……", "name": "豊川祥子"}, "figure_art": "avg_4182_oblvns_1#2$2"}, {"id": 51, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4182_oblvns_1#2$2", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 52, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "必ず、見つけ出しますわ。", "name": "豊川祥子"}, "figure_art": "avg_4182_oblvns_1#2$2"}, {"id": 53, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 54, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 55, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 56, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 57, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "bg_wilderness_n", "screenadapt": "coverall"}}, {"id": 58, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 59, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 60, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.5}}, {"id": 61, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4182_oblvns_1#12$2", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 62, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "睦、ここは現実ではありませんのよ。今すぐに……", "name": "豊川祥子"}, "figure_art": "avg_4182_oblvns_1#12$2"}, {"id": 63, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 64, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 65, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 66, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 67, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "ドン――！"}}, {"id": 68, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$bodyfalldown2", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 69, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_land_impact"}}, {"id": 70, "prop": "CameraShake", "attributes": {"duration": 0.5, "ystrength": 40.0, "vibrato": 30.0, "randomness": 90.0, "fadeout": "true", "block": "false"}}, {"id": 71, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 72, "prop": "cameraEffect", "attributes": {"effect": "Grayscale", "keep": "true", "amount": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0}}, {"id": 73, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "65_g2_dreamcastlehall", "screenadapt": "coverall", "block": "true"}}, {"id": 74, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 75, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 76, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.5}}, {"id": 77, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4182_oblvns_1#6$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 78, "prop": "CameraShake", "attributes": {"duration": 0.3, "xstrength": 10.0, "ystrength": 12.0, "vibrato": 30.0, "randomness": 30.0, "fadeout": "false"}}, {"id": 79, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "――！", "name": "豊川祥子"}, "figure_art": "avg_4182_oblvns_1#6$1"}, {"id": 80, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 81, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "心臓が激しく脈打ち、呼吸は乱れ、背中には冷や汗が滲む。"}}, {"id": 82, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "それは、あまりに散々な目覚め方だった。"}}, {"id": 83, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 84, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_gen_walk_n", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 85, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1942_1#18$1", "focus": "m", "duration": 1.0}}, {"id": 86, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 87, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "\tとってもリアルだったでしょ？", "name": "モーフィアス"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1942_1#18$1"}, {"id": 88, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1942_1#18$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 89, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "\t高いところから、地面に落ちていって……", "name": "モーフィアス"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1942_1#18$1"}, {"id": 90, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1942_1#18$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 91, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "\t夢は砕け散り、「夢なき境界」に囚われ、逃げ出すこともできない……一体、どんな感覚なのかしらね。", "name": "モーフィアス"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1942_1#18$1"}, {"id": 92, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4182_oblvns_1#9$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 93, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "皆さんの夢……確かに素敵な夢ではありましたわ。ですが、いつまでも浸っていてはいけません。", "name": "豊川祥子"}, "figure_art": "avg_4182_oblvns_1#9$1"}, {"id": 94, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4182_oblvns_1#9$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 95, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "心の一番弱い部分を覗いて、それを脚色して何度も目の前に曝け出すような……そのような夢には。", "name": "豊川祥子"}, "figure_art": "avg_4182_oblvns_1#9$1"}, {"id": 96, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1942_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 97, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "\tあら、そうかしら？", "name": "モーフィアス"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1942_1#1$1"}, {"id": 98, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1942_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 99, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "\tあんたが夢に入ってくる前は、あの子たちはあんたのことも、くだらないバンドのこともほとんど忘れちゃってたのよ。", "name": "モーフィアス"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1942_1#1$1"}, {"id": 100, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4182_oblvns_1#9$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 101, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "いいえ。Ave{@nbs}Mujicaはひとつの「契約」ですわ。皆さんの人生はわたくしが――", "name": "豊川祥子"}, "figure_art": "avg_4182_oblvns_1#9$1"}, {"id": 102, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1942_1#13$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 103, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "\tそんなもの、あんた以外にはどうだっていいの。", "name": "モーフィアス"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1942_1#13$1"}, {"id": 104, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4182_oblvns_1#4$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 105, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "なっ――！", "name": "豊川祥子"}, "figure_art": "avg_4182_oblvns_1#4$1"}, {"id": 106, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1942_1#18$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 107, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "自分の耳で聞いたでしょ？", "name": "モーフィアス"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1942_1#18$1"}, {"id": 108, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1942_1#15$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 109, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "あの子たちがあんたを拒絶するのをね。", "name": "モーフィアス"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1942_1#15$1"}, {"id": 110, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 111, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_spiritwhoosh", "volume": 0.6}}, {"id": 112, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 113, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 114, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 115, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "bg_lmstreet_1", "screenadapt": "coverall"}}, {"id": 116, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.5}}, {"id": 117, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 118, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 119, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4185_amoris_1#2$3", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 120, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "そんなのイヤ。ここにいる人たちは、みーんな女優としてのアタシを愛してくれてるの。", "name": "祐天寺にゃむ"}, "figure_art": "avg_4185_amoris_1#2$3"}, {"id": 121, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4185_amoris_1#7$3", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 122, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "アタシ、そのために何もかも捧げたんだよ？　なのに今更、全部嘘だったって言うの？", "name": "祐天寺にゃむ"}, "figure_art": "avg_4185_amoris_1#7$3"}, {"id": 123, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4185_amoris_1#2$4", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 124, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "ふざけないで。そんなの絶対認めないから！", "name": "祐天寺にゃむ"}, "figure_art": "avg_4185_amoris_1#2$4"}, {"id": 125, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4185_amoris_1#2$4", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 126, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "ここ、アタシの夢なんだよ？　アンタもバンドも関係ない。", "name": "祐天寺にゃむ"}, "figure_art": "avg_4185_amoris_1#2$4"}, {"id": 127, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 128, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_spiritwhoosh", "volume": 0.6}}, {"id": 129, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 130, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 131, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 132, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "33_g2_srcalley", "screenadapt": "coverall"}}, {"id": 133, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.5}}, {"id": 134, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 135, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 136, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4186_tmoris_1#9$3", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 137, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "あなたには分からないでしょうね。", "name": "八幡海鈴"}, "figure_art": "avg_4186_tmoris_1#9$3"}, {"id": 138, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4186_tmoris_1#9$3", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 139, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "こんな生き方でいいんです……自分には、この生き方が合っているんです。", "name": "八幡海鈴"}, "figure_art": "avg_4186_tmoris_1#9$3"}, {"id": 140, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4186_tmoris_1#3$3", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 141, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "誰にも救ってもらう必要はありません。", "name": "八幡海鈴"}, "figure_art": "avg_4186_tmoris_1#3$3"}, {"id": 142, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4186_tmoris_1#3$3", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 143, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "それに、私を救える人なんていませんので。", "name": "八幡海鈴"}, "figure_art": "avg_4186_tmoris_1#3$3"}, {"id": 144, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 145, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_spiritwhoosh", "volume": 0.6}}, {"id": 146, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 147, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 148, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 149, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "65_g4_islandharbor_n", "screenadapt": "coverall"}}, {"id": 150, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.5}}, {"id": 151, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 152, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_sea", "volume": 0.6, "loop": "true", "channel": "sea"}}, {"id": 153, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 154, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……"}}, {"id": 155, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 156, "prop": "stopSound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_sea", "fadetime": 0.5, "channel": "sea"}}, {"id": 157, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_spiritwhoosh", "volume": 0.6}}, {"id": 158, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 159, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 160, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 161, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "bg_wilderness_n", "screenadapt": "coverall"}}, {"id": 162, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.5}}, {"id": 163, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 164, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 165, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "\tやっぱり睦ちゃんには、祥子ちゃんはいらない。", "name": "「睦」"}}, {"id": 166, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 167, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 168, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 169, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 170, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "65_g2_dreamcastlehall", "screenadapt": "coverall", "block": "true"}}, {"id": 171, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 172, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 173, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.5}}, {"id": 174, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1942_1#19$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 175, "prop": "CameraShake", "attributes": {"duration": 0.3, "xstrength": 20.0, "ystrength": 20.0, "vibrato": 30.0, "randomness": 90.0, "fadeout": "true", "block": "false"}}, {"id": 176, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "あはは……あはははははっ！", "name": "モーフィアス"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1942_1#19$1"}, {"id": 177, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1942_1#19$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 178, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "\tあんたの無様で、無力で、笑える顔、全部見せてもらったわ。", "name": "モーフィアス"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1942_1#19$1"}, {"id": 179, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1942_1#18$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 180, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "最初は夢を壊されちゃったけど、これでおあいこって所かしらね。", "name": "モーフィアス"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1942_1#18$1"}, {"id": 181, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1942_1#18$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 182, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "\tふふっ、でも感謝してるわ。あんたがあの子たちの夢を何度も出入りしてくれたおかげで……", "name": "モーフィアス"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1942_1#18$1"}, {"id": 183, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1942_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 184, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "\t証明されたもの――私の作った夢が完璧で、非の打ち所がないってことが。", "name": "モーフィアス"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1942_1#1$1"}, {"id": 185, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1942_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 186, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "\tこれであいつも認めるしかないわ。私こそが夢のお城で一番の天才だってね。", "name": "モーフィアス"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1942_1#1$1"}, {"id": 187, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4182_oblvns_1#9$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 188, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "あいつ……？", "name": "豊川祥子"}, "figure_art": "avg_4182_oblvns_1#9$1"}, {"id": 189, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1942_1#5$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 190, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "\t夢の中で会ったでしょ？", "name": "モーフィアス"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1942_1#5$1"}, {"id": 191, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1942_1#17$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 192, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "\tお姫様みたいな服を着て、時代遅れの話し方をするあいつよ。", "name": "モーフィアス"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1942_1#17$1"}, {"id": 193, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1942_1#17$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 194, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "\tあいつの傍にいると、落ち着かないったらありゃしないわ。", "name": "モーフィアス"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1942_1#17$1"}, {"id": 195, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4182_oblvns_1#4$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 196, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "アイリスさんこそ夢のお城の主ですわ。あなたはただの偽物です！", "name": "豊川祥子"}, "figure_art": "avg_4182_oblvns_1#4$1"}, {"id": 197, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4182_oblvns_1#4$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 198, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "彼女はおっしゃっていました。どんな素敵な夢にも、いつかは目覚める時が来ると――", "name": "豊川祥子"}, "figure_art": "avg_4182_oblvns_1#4$1"}, {"id": 199, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4182_oblvns_1#14$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 200, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "ぐっ――！", "name": "豊川祥子"}, "figure_art": "avg_4182_oblvns_1#14$1"}, {"id": 201, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "祥子の喉は、突然凍りついたように声を発することができなくなった。"}}, {"id": 202, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1942_1#15$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 203, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "\tどうしてあんたを見ているとムカつくのか、ようやく分かったわ。", "name": "モーフィアス"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1942_1#15$1"}, {"id": 204, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1942_1#9$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 205, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "\tあんた、アイリスとそっくり。初めから他人の意見を聞く気がないし、口を開けばいつも綺麗事ばかり。", "name": "モーフィアス"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1942_1#9$1"}, {"id": 206, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1942_1#9$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 207, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "\t人生を預かるとか言ってたけど、結局みんなが自分から離れていくのが嫌なだけじゃない。", "name": "モーフィアス"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1942_1#9$1"}, {"id": 208, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1942_1#9$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 209, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "\tあんたの人生、全部見せてもらったわ。落ちぶれたお嬢様が、未練がましく足掻く姿をね。", "name": "モーフィアス"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1942_1#9$1"}, {"id": 210, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1942_1#10$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 211, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "\t自分の思い通りにしたい、他人に惨めな自分を見せたくない……あんたの行動、全部そうだったわ。", "name": "モーフィアス"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1942_1#10$1"}, {"id": 212, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1942_1#10$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 213, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "\t傲慢で、自分勝手で……ほんと救いようのない人。", "name": "モーフィアス"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1942_1#10$1"}, {"id": 214, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1942_1#16$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 215, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "\tあんたのバンドって、結局何だったの？　「契約」みたいに強い言葉で縛り付けて、バンドごっこをしていただけじゃない。", "name": "モーフィアス"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1942_1#16$1"}, {"id": 216, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1942_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 217, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "\tあの子たちは今、自分の幸せを手に入れた。だからあんたのことなんて捨てちゃったのよ。うふふっ……あんた、またひとりぼっちになっちゃったわね。", "name": "モーフィアス"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1942_1#1$1"}, {"id": 218, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1942_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 219, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "\tそれでもアイリスの言葉を信じるって言うなら……いいわ、あんたのためにもう一回素敵な夢を用意してあげる。", "name": "モーフィアス"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1942_1#1$1"}, {"id": 220, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1942_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 221, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "\tたとえ頭では現実じゃないって分かってても、ずっと見ていたくなる完璧な夢をね。", "name": "モーフィアス"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1942_1#1$1"}, {"id": 222, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1942_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 223, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "\t他の子たちと同じように、私の夢に溺れて抜け出せなくなるのよ。", "name": "モーフィアス"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1942_1#1$1"}, {"id": 224, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4182_oblvns_1#14$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 225, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "くぅっ――！", "name": "豊川祥子"}, "figure_art": "avg_4182_oblvns_1#14$1"}, {"id": 226, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1942_1#11$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 227, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "\t喋りたい？　なら最後に一言だけ喋らせてあげる。", "name": "モーフィアス"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1942_1#11$1"}, {"id": 228, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 229, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 230, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "悪魔のような少女は、鎖をほどくような手振りで空中に模様を描いた。"}}, {"id": 231, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4182_oblvns_1#4$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 232, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "わたくしは――", "name": "豊川祥子"}, "figure_art": "avg_4182_oblvns_1#4$1"}, {"id": 233, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 234, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 235, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "鎖が再び容赦なく締め上げる。"}}, {"id": 236, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1942_1#19$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 237, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "\tあはははははっ――", "name": "モーフィアス"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1942_1#19$1"}, {"id": 238, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1942_1#18$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 239, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "\tやっぱりあんた、黙ってる時の方がずっと可愛いわ！", "name": "モーフィアス"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1942_1#18$1"}, {"id": 240, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "もがき続ける祥子にモーフィアスは一歩ずつ近づき、右手を伸ばして祥子の頬に添えた。"}}, {"id": 241, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1942_1#18$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 242, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "\t偽りのお姫様。あんたが不思議の国を彷徨ってる間に、私ははっきり理解したわ。", "name": "モーフィアス"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1942_1#18$1"}, {"id": 243, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1942_1#18$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 244, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "\tあんたが何をに飢えて、何を求めて、何を恐れているかをね。", "name": "モーフィアス"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1942_1#18$1"}, {"id": 245, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1942_1#18$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 246, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "\tだから心配しないで。今度は完璧な夢を見せてあげる。夢の中だってはっきり分かってるのに、絶対に目覚めたくならないやつをね。", "name": "モーフィアス"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1942_1#18$1"}, {"id": 247, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1942_1#17$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 248, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": " おやすみなさい。高貴で、狡猾で、自分勝手なお人形さん。", "name": "モーフィアス"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1942_1#17$1"}, {"id": 249, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1942_1#17$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 250, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "\t良い夢を。", "name": "モーフィアス"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1942_1#17$1"}, {"id": 251, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 252, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {"fadetime": 2.0}}, {"id": 253, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 254, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 3.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 255, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 256, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 257, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "ガタン、ゴトン。"}}, {"id": 258, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "祥子、祥子！", "name": "？？？"}}, {"id": 259, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 260, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 261, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "ん……", "name": "豊川祥子"}}, {"id": 262, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 263, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "46_g1_transporter", "screenadapt": "coverall", "block": "true"}}, {"id": 264, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 265, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 266, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 267, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4182_oblvns_1#4$2", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 268, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "あなたの言うようになんて――", "name": "豊川祥子"}, "figure_art": "avg_4182_oblvns_1#4$2"}, {"id": 269, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 270, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "祥子は思わず叫んだが、そこはもう城の中ではなく、モーフィアスも姿を消していた。"}}, {"id": 271, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 272, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_290_vigna_1#4$1", "focus": "m", "duration": 1.0}}, {"id": 273, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 274, "prop": "PlayMusic", "attributes": {"intro": "$mist_intro", "key": "$mist_loop", "volume": 0.6}}, {"id": 275, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "\t大丈夫？　顔色すごく悪いよ。また悪夢でも見たの？", "name": "ヴィグナ"}, "figure_art": "avg_290_vigna_1#4$1"}, {"id": 276, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4182_oblvns_1#14$2", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 277, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "また……夢の中に戻ってきましたのね。", "name": "豊川祥子"}, "figure_art": "avg_4182_oblvns_1#14$2"}, {"id": 278, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_290_vigna_1#4$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 279, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "\tなに訳分かんないこと言ってんの、今起きたとこでしょ。", "name": "ヴィグナ"}, "figure_art": "avg_290_vigna_1#4$1"}, {"id": 280, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_290_vigna_1#4$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 281, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "\tもしかして、まだ寝ぼけてる？", "name": "ヴィグナ"}, "figure_art": "avg_290_vigna_1#4$1"}, {"id": 282, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4182_oblvns_1#6$2", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 283, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "アイリスさんとベナさんもいらっしゃるのね……", "name": "豊川祥子"}, "figure_art": "avg_4182_oblvns_1#6$2"}, {"id": 284, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_338_iris_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 285, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "はじめまして……自己紹介はまだですわよね？", "name": "アイリス"}, "figure_art": "avg_338_iris_1#1$1"}, {"id": 286, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_369_bena_1#5$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 287, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "ええ、あたしたちが着いた時にはもう寝てたわ。", "name": "ベナ"}, "figure_art": "avg_369_bena_1#5$1"}, {"id": 288, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4182_oblvns_1#6$2", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 289, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "ヴィグナさんとわたくしが先に乗り込んでいるということは……新しい夢に切り替わった、ということですのね……", "name": "豊川祥子"}, "figure_art": "avg_4182_oblvns_1#6$2"}, {"id": 290, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_290_vigna_1#11$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 291, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "\t祥子、何さっきから変なことばっかり――", "name": "ヴィグナ"}, "figure_art": "avg_290_vigna_1#11$1"}, {"id": 292, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 293, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 294, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 295, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.6, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 296, "prop": "Subtitle", "attributes": {"text": "今は、アイリスさんのお知り合いのアンさんを訪ねるため、ヴィクトリアの小さな街へ向かっているところ……", "x": 300.0, "y": 350.0, "alignment": "center", "size": 24.0, "delay": 0.04, "width": 700.0}}, {"id": 297, "prop": "Subtitle", "attributes": {"text": "けれど、すぐにタイヤがパンクして修理のために待機することになり、それで到着も遅れてしまう……", "x": 300.0, "y": 350.0, "alignment": "center", "size": 24.0, "delay": 0.04, "width": 700.0}}, {"id": 298, "prop": "subtitle", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 299, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 300, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 301, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4182_oblvns_1#14$2", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 302, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "わたくしたち、これからヴィクトリアへアンさんを探しに行きますのよね？", "name": "豊川祥子"}, "figure_art": "avg_4182_oblvns_1#14$2"}, {"id": 303, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_290_vigna_1#11$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 304, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "\tえっ、アンさんって誰？　アイリスは知ってる？", "name": "ヴィグナ"}, "figure_art": "avg_290_vigna_1#11$1"}, {"id": 305, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_338_iris_1#4$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 306, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "アンさん……？　祥子さんのお友達ですの？", "name": "アイリス"}, "figure_art": "avg_338_iris_1#4$1"}, {"id": 307, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4182_oblvns_1#14$2", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 308, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "えっ……アンさんをご存知ありませんの？", "name": "豊川祥子"}, "figure_art": "avg_4182_oblvns_1#14$2"}, {"id": 309, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4182_oblvns_1#10$2", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 310, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "では、わたくしとヴィグナさんは何のために……？", "name": "豊川祥子"}, "figure_art": "avg_4182_oblvns_1#10$2"}, {"id": 311, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_290_vigna_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 312, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "\tちょうど仕事の場所が祥子の家の近くなんでしょ？　だからついでに家に帰って、家族のもとで休んでもらおうと思ってるの。", "name": "ヴィグナ"}, "figure_art": "avg_290_vigna_1#1$1"}, {"id": 313, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_290_vigna_1#5$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 314, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": " 仕事が忙しくて、ずっと家に帰ってなかっただろうしね。", "name": "ヴィグナ"}, "figure_art": "avg_290_vigna_1#5$1"}, {"id": 315, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 316, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 317, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$drift", "volume": 0.6}}, {"id": 318, "prop": "CameraShake", "attributes": {"duration": 2.0, "xstrength": 20.0, "ystrength": 20.0, "vibrato": 30.0, "randomness": 90.0, "fadeout": "true", "block": "false"}}, {"id": 319, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 320, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_338_iris_1#4$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 321, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "車が急に止まりましたわ！　何事ですの！？", "name": "アイリス"}, "figure_art": "avg_338_iris_1#4$1"}, {"id": 322, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_369_bena_1#5$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 323, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "まさか、パンク！？", "name": "ベナ"}, "figure_art": "avg_369_bena_1#5$1"}, {"id": 324, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 325, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "はぁ、はぁ……あ、危うく駄獣にぶつかるところでした！", "name": "運転手"}, "figure_art": "avg_369_bena_1#5$1"}, {"id": 326, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "幸い何事もありませんでした。すぐに再出発します！", "name": "運転手"}, "figure_art": "avg_369_bena_1#5$1"}, {"id": 327, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4182_oblvns_1#10$2", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 328, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……", "name": "豊川祥子"}, "figure_art": "avg_4182_oblvns_1#10$2"}, {"id": 329, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 330, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "エンジンがかかる音と共に、窓の外の景色が再び動き出した。"}}, {"id": 331, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 332, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 333, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 334, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 335, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "bg_wilderness_d", "screenadapt": "coverall", "block": "true"}}, {"id": 336, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.5}}, {"id": 337, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 338, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.5}}, {"id": 339, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "同じ景色、同じ同行者。"}}, {"id": 340, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "しかし夢の中では、すでに変化が起こっていた。"}}, {"id": 341, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 342, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 343, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {"fadetime": 2.0}}, {"id": 344, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 345, "prop": "Image", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 346, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": ""}}], "OPTIONTRACE": true}